metadata.name: “The  Calila e Dimna” - Part 1
metadata.description: There was a huge library at the order’s headquarters. The alien took an old book out and began reading: “An obese cat was telling a skinny cat that he gets his food from the royal kitchen only and eats roasted turkey. Having no image of such delicious food, the skinny cat imagined the other laying on a throne and being brought gigantic roasted turkeys by mice, and the king personally preparing him delicious meals.”
